# KCIC Brand Palette

## Canonical colors (only approved brand hues)

| Name | Hex | Use |
|------|-----|-----|
| Green | `#80C738` | Primary actions, active states, success |
| Gray | `#8B8D90` | Secondary text, labels, subdued UI |
| White | `#FFFFFF` | Surfaces, cards, inverted button text |
| Blue | `#00ADDD` | Links, info, content taxonomy |
| Brown | `#E97451` | Warm highlights, featured callouts |

## Rules

- Do **not** use legacy forest (`#006B45`), ink (`#111827`), shell blue (`#F6F8FF`), or other off-palette brand colors.
- Derive borders, panels, and disabled states from Gray + White only (see `DESIGN.md`).
- Primary text: darkened Gray (`#4A4B4D`). Danger/error may use standard red outside the five brand hues.
- Read `DESIGN.md` before UI or email work.

